snippet.textDisplay: Finally a song showcasing the essence of female power, strength and endurance. I absolutely loved this song it has the potential to become huge. Let's honor and respect all women around us and promote this culture of tolerance instead of merely humming along with these wonderful singers. Shamu bai's voice is absolutely beautiful. It's so raw and rich it leaves you enchanted. The Kalasha girls are adorable with their sweet voices. They have a bright future hopefully we'll see them more. I have always been a fan of Rachel Viccaji. Her vocals are mind blowing please give her a solo song in Coke Studio soon. I am waiting for that day eagerly.
